App Shell (Application Shell) 
------------------------------
architecture is one way to build PWA (Progressive web Apps).
The App shell is the minimum (HTML,CSS and Javascript ) required to power the user Interface when 
cached Offline, Can ensure reliably good performance. 

Service workder
----------------
For SPA (Single Page Applications) with heavy Javascript applications this App Shell approach
aggressivly depends on Service workder (for caching the shell).

PWA (Progressive Web Apps):
---------------------------
Charectarstics of PWA. 
  1. Reliable -> Loads instantly, even with bad network conditions
  2. Fast -> Responds quickly to user interactions 
  3. Engaging -> Feels like natual app on the device ( user engagements like push notification, Readly opened from desktop etc.. )
